description:
Is globalization good or bad? 
There are countless problems with our world today. Perhaps globalization is the answer to the world's problems. According to some world leaders, it is. The concept might sound good, but is a worldwide unification actually a good thing? 
Globalization is nothing new. In the Book of Daniel, we read about Nebuchadnezzar, who sought world domination. There are many parallels between Nebuchadnezzar's story and what God's remnant will experience in the last days. Join Hal Mayer as he explores the lessons we can learn from this story and discovers the truth about globalization.
